data.text:
@secresdoge [1/3]Hallo Sebastian, 
Vielen Dank für deine Nachricht! Die Lufthansa Group hat eine eigene Risikobewertung 
vorgenommen mit dem Ergebnis, dass Tracker mit sehr geringer Batterie- und Sendeleistung im aufgegebenen Gepäck kein Sicherheitsrisiko darstellen.

@botoxandmash Hello Cat,
We're glad you enjoyed your trip with us! :)
Best regards, Gayle

@LorenaM18293368 Hello Lorena, 
I'm sorry you haven't received a response yet. Our colleagues are confronted with a high amount of requests at the moment and this makes it difficult for them to keep the usual average response time. We kindly ask for your continued patience. 
Best regards, Gayle

@MauGentile @Lufthansa_DE Hello,
We are very sorry about your delayed luggage. Please turn to the contact from your missing luggage report. Unfortunately, we, the Social Media Team, can not assist with tracking missing luggage. We kindly ask for your understanding.
Best regards, Gayle

@mrs_lunaa Hello Luna, 
This should not have happened and I can only profusely apologize. Have you already contacted the office stated on your missing luggage report for further assistance? 
Best regards, Gayle

@camillacaros Hello Camilla,
Kindly send us the reference number on your Passenger Irregularity Report via DM; we will try and have a closer look. 
Best regards, Gayle

@duzdanisaq @lufthansa Hello there, 
We are very sorry about your delayed luggage. Please turn to the contact from your missing luggage report. Unfortunately, we, the Social Media Team, can not assist with tracking missing luggage. We kindly ask for your understanding.
Best regards, Gayle

@mrs_lunaa Hello Luna, 
I'm sorry to hear your luggage wasn't duly delivered. Please be assured that our colleagues are working around the clock to process each bag and reunite passengers with their luggage. We kindly ask for your patience.
Best regards, Gayle

@dastoyvr Hello Daniel,
Due to the considerable amount of inquiries sent to us, you may experience longer waiting times at the moment. My colleagues are doing their best and will reply to your concern as soon as they possibly can. 
Best regards, Gayle

@8ball25  Hello,
we would be happy to help you in this case. Please feel free to DM us your case number and we'd be happy to assist.
Kind regards, Alessandra

@Tiltb0y Hello,
Depending on your request upon check-in, you can either ask for the stroller to be offloaded in Vienna and delivered to the aircraft door, or advise my colleagues to have it tagged to your final destination. 
Best regards, Gayle

@Tiltb0y Hi there, 
Thanks for your message! The minimum connecting time in Vienna is 25 minutes. This time is enough to transfer from one gate to the next, if you already checked in for your connecting flight, provided there are no flight delays. 
Best regards, Gayle

@r8lobster Hello,
We are very sorry about your delayed luggage. Please turn to the contact from your missing luggage report. We - the Social Media Team, can unfortunately not assist with tracking missing luggage. We kindly ask for your understanding.
Best regards, Gayle

@philippedavidny Dear Philippe,
the team is working through a large volume of claims at present and will do their best to get to yours as soon as they can. Again, I really do appreciate your frustration.
Best regards, Alessandra
